data.description: This home is absolutely beautiful and has been updated with a brand new roof (2022) hardwood flooring throughout the entire home.  New ceiling fans in this home are a great addition to the central air.  Front porch that you can sit out on and enjoy the weather. Brand new backsplash, New Wall Mount Range Hood,  Two full bathrooms, one upstairs on main bedroom floor and one full in the partially finished basement that was made into a 4th bedroom.  There is a fully secure walk out door of basement that leads in and out to the two car driveway.  Brand new wrought iron first front door with locks and then secondary wooden door.  Great lighting in front room to enjoy on sunny days!!!  Keypad lock on basement door and outer basement door.  Very large set of three closets in master bedroom.  Seller has loved the home since 2019 where she renovated tons of things in the home including new crown molding.
